            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2 group-hover:text-coral-600 transition-colors">Advisory Services</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Strategic relocation consulting, tax planning, and comprehensive relocation support.</p>
